Include bookworm-security so you receive timely CVE fixes.  

bookworm-updates pulls important fixes that must ship before the next point release.  

Only un‑comment bookworm-backports when you intend to install specific newer packages.  

Add components you actually use; leaving out unneeded non-free* reduces noise and risk.




